OL,3,C'I thought I was going to die', says
OL,4,Cyouth worker stabbed at school
OL,6,F"It just happened. It's just what I
OL,7,Fdid. I wasn't thinking about anything
OL,8,Fspecifically. I don't think anyone can
OL,9,Fprepare for how they're going to
OL,10,Frespond in that situation and if it
OL,11,Fhappened again would I respond the
OL,12,Fsame? I have no idea."
OL,14,FMs Bulmer managed to calm Mellotte
OL,15,Fdown and waited with him until police
OL,16,Farrived.
OL,18,FShe and the other victims escaped the
OL,19,Fattack with minor injuries but says it
OL,20,Fcould have turned out very differently.
