OL,6,FA Freedom of Information request
OL,7,Frevealed there were 245 knives or
OL,8,Fbladed articles found in the county's
OL,9,Fschools since 2018 - an average of one
OL,10,Fevery ten days.
OL,12,FMeanwhile in 2024 there were 713
OL,13,Fassaults in South Yorkshire schools, a
OL,14,Frise of 45% compared to five years ago.
OL,16,FThe findings come on the day Sheffield
OL,17,Fteenager Harvey Wilgoose's killer was
OL,18,Ffound guilty of his murder.
